==製取及培養==
L型細菌能在實驗室中以許多有細胞壁的細菌為原料製備。比如枯草芽孢桿菌、[[大腸桿菌|大腸桿菌]]都可以用來製備L型細菌。通過抑制肽的合成可以製備L型細菌，而前者通常是通過用[[抗生素|抗生素]]或能夠水解細菌細胞壁的[[溶菌酶|溶菌酶]]對細菌進行處理達成的。為了防止菌體因過渡吸水而裂解，L型細菌通常會在與其[[細胞質基質|細胞質基質]]具有相同{{link-en|摩爾滲透壓|osmolarity}}的培養液（即[[滲透壓|等滲]]培養液）中培養<ref name=Joseleau/>。L型細菌在製成後可重新長出細胞壁，但可將之長期置於製備環境中避免<ref>{{cite journal |author=Allan EJ |title=Induction and cultivation of a stable L-form of Bacillus subtilis |journal=J. Appl. Bacteriol. |volume=70 |issue=4 |pages=339–43 |date=April 1991 |pmid=1905284 |doi=10.1111/j.1365-2672.1991.tb02946.x}}</ref>。

一些研究指出，L型細菌發生了突變，因為它們是由正常的細菌衍生而來的<ref name="pmid123455"/><ref name=Joseleau/>。该突变点为一種参与{{link-en|脂質代謝|lipid metabolism}}[[甲羥戊酸途徑|甲羥戊酸途徑]]的酶。上述突變據信能夠將生成L型細菌的可能性提高至原來的1000倍<ref name="pmid123455"/>。這種突變對L型細菌產生影響的機制尚不明確。不過有人推斷該突變影響的酶可能与一種和肽聚糖合成關係密切的脂質生成中扮演着重要角色，因而提高了正常細菌向L型細菌轉化的可能性。

另外，還有一種利用[[納米技術|納米技術]]的誘導L型細菌的方法。實驗者首先使用[[微流體|微流體]]設備對細菌施加空間限制，進而抑制肽聚糖合成。再經由一個狹窄（亞微米級）的连接两个生境的生物廊道之後，L型細菌就可生成<ref>{{cite journal |author=Männik J., R. Driessen, P. Galajda, J.E. Keymer, C. Dekker |title=Bacterial growth and motility in sub-micron constrictions |journal= PNAS |volume=106 |issue=35 |pages=14861–14866 |date=September 2009 |pmid= 19706420| doi=10.1073/pnas.0907542106 |pmc=2729279}}</ref>。

==意義和應用==
部分出版物稱L型細菌可能會引起人類<ref>{{cite journal | author=Wall S, Kunze ZM, Saboor S, Soufleri I, Seechurn P, Chiodini R, McFadden JJ | title=Identification of spheroplast-like agents isolated from tissues of patients with Crohn's disease and control tissues by polymerase chain reaction | journal=J Clin Microbiol | volume=31 | issue=5 | pages=1241–5 | year=1993 | pmid=8501224 | url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC262911/pdf/jcm00017-0237.pdf | pmc=262911 | access-date=2014-11-28 | archive-date=2022-01-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220122175953/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC262911/pdf/jcm00017-0237.pdf }}</ref>及其它動物的疾病<ref>{{cite journal | author=Hulten K, Karttunen TJ, El-Zimaity HM, Naser SA, Collins MT, Graham DY, El-Zaatari FA |title=Identification of cell wall deficient forms of M. avium subsp. paratuberculosis in paraffin embedded tissues from animals with Johne's disease by in situ hybridization |pmid=11018275
| year=2000 | volume=42 | issue=2 | pages=185–95 | journal=J Microbiol Methods | doi=10.1016/S0167-7012(00)00185-8}}</ref>。因為有關L型細菌能致病的證據很零碎而且常常自相矛盾，所以上述說法尚未得到學界的一致認可<ref>{{cite journal |author=Onwuamaegbu ME, Belcher RA, Soare C |title=Cell wall-deficient bacteria as a cause of infections: a review of the clinical significance |journal=J. Int. Med. Res. |volume=33 |issue=1 |pages=1–20 |year=2005 |pmid=15651712 |url=http://www.jimronline.net/content/full/2005/58/0545.pdf |doi=10.1177/147323000503300101 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090824140149/http://www.jimronline.net/content/full/2005/58/0545.pdf |archivedate=2009-08-24 |access-date=2014-11-28 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author=Casadesús J |title=Bacterial L-forms require peptidoglycan synthesis for cell division |journal=BioEssays |volume=29 |issue=12 |pages=1189–91 |date=December 2007 |pmid=18008373 |doi=10.1002/bies.20680}}</ref>。關於L型細菌的致病性問題，有兩種互相對立的觀點，其中一種觀點認為L性細菌完全沒有研究價值，因為它們完全沒有臨床意義；而另外一種觀點的持有者則認為，L型細菌具有重要意義但還沒有引起人們重視的致病性<ref name=Domingue/>。有關L型細菌的研究仍在進行。科學家在接種了{{link-en|諾卡氏菌|Nocardia}}小鼠的肺部中觀察到了L型細菌<ref>{{cite journal |author=Beaman BL |title=Induction of L-phase variants of Nocardia caviae within intact murine lungs |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_infection-and-immunity_1980-07_29_1/page/244 |journal=Infect. Immun. |volume=29 |issue=1 |pages=244–51 |date=July 1980 |pmid=7399704 |pmc=551102 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author=Beaman BL, Scates SM |title=Role of L-forms of Nocardia caviae in the development of chronic mycetomas in normal and immunodeficient murine models |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_infection-and-immunity_1981-09_33_3/page/893 |journal=Infect. Immun. |volume=33 |issue=3 |pages=893–907 |date=September 1981 |pmid=7287189 |pmc=350795 }}</ref>。另外，一項發佈於2001年的研究報告指出，接受[[造血幹細胞移植|造血幹細胞移植]]患者在[[免疫抑制|免疫被抑制]]期間可能會被L型細菌感染<ref>{{cite journal |author=Woo PC, Wong SS, Lum PN, Hui WT, Yuen KY |title=Cell-wall-deficient bacteria and culture-negative febrile episodes in bone-marrow-transplant recipients |journal=Lancet |volume=357 |issue=9257 |pages=675–9 |date=March 2001 |pmid=11247551 |doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(00)04131-3}}</ref>。另外，還有人提出沒有細胞壁的L型細菌可能在細菌獲得[[抗藥性|對抗生素的抗性]]的研究中具重要意義<ref>{{cite journal |author=Fuller E, Elmer C, Nattress F, ''et al'' |title=β-Lactam Resistance in Staphylococcus aureus Cells That Do Not Require a Cell Wall for Integrity |journal=Antimicrob. Agents Chemother. |volume=49 |issue=12 |pages=5075–80 |date=December 2005 |pmid=16304175 |pmc=1315936 |doi=10.1128/AAC.49.12.5075-5080.2005 |url=http://aac.asm.org/cgi/content/full/49/12/5075#R10 |access-date=2014-11-28 |archive-date=2009-05-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090529053802/http://aac.asm.org/cgi/content/full/49/12/5075#R10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

L型細菌可能對有關早期的生命形式以及[[生命科技|生命科技]]的研究起到一定作用。科學家努力讓L型細菌成為生命科技中能[[蛋白質合成|表達]][[基因工程|重組基因]]的受體<ref>{{cite journal |author=Sieben, Stefan |title=Die stabilen Protoplasten-Typ L-Formen von Proteus mirabilis als neues Expressionssystem für sekretorische Proteine und integrale Mempranproteine |journal=Dissertation Universität Jena, April 1998, OCLC-Nummer: 246350676 | url=http://www.worldcat.org/oclc/246350676 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author=Sieben S, Hertle R, Gumpert J, Braun V. |title=The Serratia marcescens hemolysin is secreted but not activated by stable protoplast-type L-forms of Proteus mirabilis. |journal=Arch Microbiol. |volume=170 |issue=4 |pages=236-42. |date=October 1998 |pmid=9732437 |doi=10.1007/s002030050638}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author=Gumpert J, Hoischen C |title=Use of cell wall-less bacteria (L-forms) for efficient expression and secretion of heterologous gene products |journal=Current Opinion in Biotechnology |volume=9 |issue=5 |pages=506–9 |date=October 1998 |pmid=9821280 |doi=10.1016/S0958-1669(98)80037-2}}</ref>。L型細菌很適合作為重組基因的受體，因為他們能夠產生大量的分泌蛋白，而且這些分泌蛋白不會像在有細胞壁的細菌中那樣堆積在[[週質空間|週質空間]]中（分泌蛋白在週質空間中的積累可能會對細菌造成毒害作用，從而造成蛋白質產率的降低）<ref>{{cite journal |author=Rippmann JF, Klein M, Hoischen C, ''et al'' |title=Procaryotic Expression of Single-Chain Variable-Fragment (scFv) Antibodies: Secretion in L-Form Cells of Proteus mirabilis Leads to Active Product and Overcomes the Limitations of Periplasmic Expression in Escherichia coli |journal=Appl. Environ. Microbiol. |volume=64 |issue=12 |pages=4862–9 |date=1 December 1998 |pmid=9835575 |pmc=90935 |url=http://aem.asm.org/cgi/pmidlookup?view=long&pmid=9835575 |access-date=2014-11-28 |archive-date=2019-10-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191018061531/https://aem.asm.org/content/64/12/4862.long |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author=Choi JH, Lee SY |title=Secretory and extracellular production of recombinant proteins using Escherichia coli |journal=Appl. Microbiol. Biotechnol. |volume=64 |issue=5 |pages=625–35 |date=June 2004 |pmid=14966662 |doi=10.1007/s00253-004-1559-9}}</ref>。

